sourcesContent: import React from 'react' export default function StateWiseData(props) { var confirm = props.data.total; var active = confirm - props.data.deaths - props.data.recovered; return( {props.data.state} {props.data.delta_total === 0?"": `(+${props.data.delta_total})`} {confirm} {props.data.delta_active === 0?"": `(+${props.data.delta_active})`} {active} {props.data.delta_recovered === 0?"": `(+${props.data.delta_recovered})`} {props.data.recovered} {props.data.delta_deaths === 0?"": `(+${props.data.delta_deaths})`} {props.data.deaths} ) }
